GET /api/storymaps?page=1&limit=10 需要返回格式：
[
  {
    "storyMapId": string,
    "title": string,
    "description": string,
    "authorID": uuid-string,
    "createdAt": timestamp,
    "updatedAt": timestamp,
    "likes": int,
    "comments" string,
    "lat": double,
    "lng": double,
    "category": string,
    "location": string,
    "author" : string
  },
  ...
]
